# Migration / schema change — STOP

New migrations are on the hard-rules list. Do **not** silently proceed.

- Surface this to the user and recommend an Opus (max-thinking) turn before writing the file.
- RLS policies, backfills, and PHI columns must not be guessed — confirm the approach first.
- If continuing, follow @docs/Reference/engineering/development/MIGRATIONS_AND_CHANGE.md exactly, and keep the change additive/reversible where possible.
